<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>内部导航门户</title>
<style>
* {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
}

body {
    font-family: "微软雅黑", "PingFang SC", sans-serif;
    background-color: #f0f2f5;
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 60px 20px;
}

.container {
    max-width: 1000px;
    margin: 0 auto;
}

.top-title {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
}

.top-title h1 {
    font-size: 36px;
    color: #1f2937;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
}

.top-title p {
    color: #6b7280;
    font-size: 16px;
}

/* 宫格布局 两排/四格一排 自由调 */
.grid-box {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
}

.grid-item {
    background: #ffffff;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 40px 20px;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.06);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    text-decoration: none;
}

.grid-item:hover {
    transform: translateY(-6px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
}

.grid-item h3 {
    font-size: 20px;
    color: #1f2937;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
}

.grid-item span {
    font-size: 14px;
    color: #6b7280;
}

.footer {
    text-align: center;
    margin-top: 60px;
    color: #9ca3af;
    font-size: 13px;
}

/* 适配手机 自动变单列 */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
    .grid-box {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    <div class="top-title">
        <h1>内部综合导航门户</h1>
        <p>内网系统 · 快速访问入口 · 内部专用</p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid-box">
        <!-- 内部链接 自行改地址和文字 -->
        <a class="grid-item" href="http://192.168.1.100">
            <h3>内部业务系统</h3>
            <span>日常办公业务入口</span>
        </a>

        <a class="grid-item" href="http://192.168.1.101">
            <h3>文件共享服务</h3>
            <span>内部资料/文件存储</span>
        </a>

        <a class="grid-item" href="http://192.168.1.102">
            <h3>管理后台</h3>
            <span>系统管理与配置</span>
        </a>

        <a class="grid-item" href="http://192.168.1.103">
            <h3>监控运维平台</h3>
            <span>设备状态全网监控</span>
        </a>

        <a class="grid-item" href="https://daiw86112-ship-it.github.io/new2/">
            <h3>子页面入口</h3>
            <span>个人拓展页面</span>
        </a>

        <a class="grid-item" href="#">
            <h3>预留站点</h3>
            <span>待添加内部系统</span>
        </a>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
        内部专属导航系统 © 2026
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
